{"tid":2494601,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有無人分手真係純分手?","createTime":"2021-04-18T16:17:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T19:48:17.000Z","uid":346655,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0279029b516174f69f3e45535ed809ce8e8d2345","tid":2494601,"uid":346655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T16:17:31.000Z","msg":"見襯啲朋友分手，口講就話係和平分手，但無耐其中一方就好快搵嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(佢哋本身拍咗以年計嘅拖，但其中一方散咗3-4個月就有新人)<br />\n<br />\n其實分手係咪主要都係因為遇到個更好嘅人先會分? 定係真係有人係和平散得嚟真係一段時間無拍拖? 或者大家講下覺得散咗幾耐先拍翻拖算無重疊到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f78aaa538f47b3d25669470bbb6c407bfe50e80","tid":2494601,"uid":125168,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T16:19:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279f9d42c63341bfbbbb244a956c5e406b96758f","tid":2494601,"uid":202151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T16:44:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283dbd3be5e0c7a5678ca7fbf6fd196819be3ea2","tid":2494601,"uid":240682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T18:10:48.000Z","msg":"有人咁快搵下一個 可能係當水泡治療情傷既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e24ad60e94386eae7798837a0d1c9917590253","tid":2494601,"uid":12270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"279f9d42c63341bfbbbb244a956c5e406b96758f","tid":2494601,"uid":202151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T16:44:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T18:59:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c89ae283d359d2a1251873e685d3e1793d84263","tid":2494601,"uid":353692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T19:16:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0cb2b741f55a5bdef2d620bb4e24fbb50886227","tid":2494601,"uid":228213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T19:48:17.000Z","msg":"通常多選擇既都好快搵到既。<br />\n<br />\n遇到個更好嘅人係個誘因，<br />\n同時都係對而家呢個唔滿意。"}]}